# API Configuration
# Backend API URL (for local development)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# ============================================
# VERCEL DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================
# 1. Deploy the backend first:
#    cd backend
#    vercel
#    Note the deployment URL (e.g., https://azovis-backend.vercel.app)
#
# 2. Deploy the frontend:
#    cd frontend
#    vercel
#
# 3. Set environment variables in Vercel dashboard for frontend:
#    - NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL: Your backend Vercel URL
#      (e.g., https://azovis-backend.vercel.app)
#
# 4. Update backend ALLOWED_ORIGINS:
#    - Go to your backend project in Vercel
#    - Settings > Environment Variables
#    - Add/update ALLOWED_ORIGINS to include your frontend URL
#    - Example: https://azovis-frontend.vercel.app
#
# 5. Redeploy backend to apply CORS changes
# ============================================
